@startuml
' Scope: production runtime topology
' Related: FR-NTF-01, FR-NTF-02, NFR-REL-01
title katekyo 配置図

actor "Web / PWA user" as User

node "Vercel" {
  artifact "Next.js application" as App
  component "Serverless Functions\nServer Actions / Route Handlers" as Functions
  component "Scheduled invocation\nVercel Cron (plan dependent)" as Cron
  App --> Functions
  Cron --> Functions : Bearer CRON_SECRET
}

database "Supabase PostgreSQL" as Postgres
folder "Supabase Storage\nhomework-photos" as Storage
cloud "LINE Platform" as Line
cloud "Upstash QStash" as Qstash

User --> App : HTTPS
Functions --> Postgres : Prisma / TLS
Functions --> Storage : service credential / HTTPS
Functions --> Line : Messaging API / HTTPS
Functions --> Qstash : schedule / cancel
Qstash --> Functions : signed webhook / HTTPS
Line --> Functions : signed webhook / HTTPS

note bottom of Functions
  秘密情報は環境変数で管理する。
  Webhook/Cronは署名またはBearerを検証し、
  reminderSentAtで冪等性を確保する。
end note
@enduml

